---
import PageLayout from '../../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Privacy policy | Académie Évolution"
  description="How we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
  lang="en"
>
  <section class="relative z-20 border-0">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
      <span class="tag anim-fade-up" style="--delay:.2s">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter mt-4 anim-slide-l" style="--delay:.35s">Privacy policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/60 mt-3 anim-fade-up" style="--delay:.5s">Last updated: March 17, 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-12 space-y-8 text-sm text-white/65 leading-relaxed">
        <div class="reveal" style="--delay:.1s">
          <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">1. Information we collect</h2>
          <p>We collect information you provide (name, email, phone, coaching-related data) and certain data collected automatically (device, usage, cookies). We may also receive data via third-party integrations (e.g. Apple Health or connected devices) if you enable them.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal" style="--delay:.15s">
          <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">2. How we use your data</h2>
          <p>We use your data to deliver coaching, personalize training and nutrition, improve the site and app, communicate about your program, and process payments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal" style="--delay:.2s">
          <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">3. Sharing</h2>
          <p>We don’t sell your personal data. We may share limited information with service providers (payment, hosting, analytics) strictly to operate the service, under strict data protection agreements.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal" style="--delay:.25s">
          <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">4. Security</h2>
          <p>We apply standard security measures (encryption, secure servers, access controls). No internet transmission is 100% secure.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal" style="--delay:.3s">
          <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">5. Your rights</h2>
          <p>You may request access, correction, or deletion of your data. You may also export data from the app where applicable. Contact <a href="mailto:info@academieevolution.com" class="underline hover:text-white transition">info@academieevolution.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal" style="--delay:.35s">
          <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">6. Cookies</h2>
          <p>We use essential cookies and, where applicable, analytics cookies. See our <a href="/en/cookies/" class="underline hover:text-white transition">cookie policy</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal" style="--delay:.4s">
          <h2 class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">7. Contact</h2>
          <p>Questions: <a href="mailto:info@academieevolution.com" class="underline hover:text-white transition">info@academieevolution.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
